.TH SNAP-L10N 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "Snap L10n Manual"
.SH NAME
snap-l10n - View snap package translation status
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B snap-l10n
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBsnap-l10n\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita application for viewing translation status of installed Snap packages. It lists installed snaps with their translation status, queries the snapd API, checks .desktop files for translations, shows present and missing languages per snap, provides color-coded status, and links to the Snap Store.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
.TP
.B Ctrl+Q
Quit the application
.TP
.B F5
Refresh the current data
.TP
.B Ctrl+/
Show keyboard shortcuts dialog
.TP
.B Ctrl+E
Export current view to CSV or JSON format
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/snap-l10n/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/snap-l10n/
Cached data.
